comments: Redick (PHI) is in the lane for at or about three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
During the pick, Randle (NOP) initiates contact with Redick (PHI) that affects his ability to obtain position.
Marjanovic (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Jackson (NOP) and gives him room to avoid contact.
Marjanovic (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Payton (NOP) and gives him room to avoid contact.
Payton (NOP) makes marginal contact to the body of Butler (PHI) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Jackson (NOP) gives Redick (PHI) room to land on the jump shot attempt.
Jackson (NOP) briefly grasps Simmons (PHI) during the pick but does not affect his FOM.
RAR shows Diallo (NOP) makes contact with Marjanovic's (PHI) body causing him to lose possession of the ball.
Marjanovic (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position on Holiday (NOP) and cleanly dislodges the ball during his drive.
Scott (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Payton (NOP) and gives him room to avoid contact.
Scott (PHI) makes contact with Holiday (NOP) that affects his ability to retrieve the ball.
Payton (NOP) makes some contact with Redick (PHI) during the pick but does not prevent him from disengaging from the marginal contact.
Scott (PHI) does not give Payton (NOP) a step to avoid contact but he is able to move through the slight contact.
LLB shows Diallo (NOP) makes incidental hand-on-ball contact during Butler's (PHI) driving shot attempt.
Scott (PHI) makes contact to the arm of Holiday (NOP) on the drive that affects his SQBR.
Simmons (PHI) moves laterally into the path of Holiday (NOP) on the drive and the contact affects his SQBR.
Holiday (NOP) commits a take foul on Harris (PHI).
Randle (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Simmons (PHI) and absorbs the contact.
Harris (PHI) makes marginal contact to the body of Randle (NOP) during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
Randle (NOP) commits a take foul on Simmons (PHI).
Butler (PHI) makes incidental contact to the arm of Moore (NOP) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
RLS shows Payton (NOP) makes contact with the ball and then incidental body contact with Scott (PHI) that does not affect his ability to retrieve the rebound.
RLS shows Scott (PHI) grabs Randle's (NOP) arm during the rebound and affects his ability to retrieve the ball.
